content.rendered:
Directed by Abhinay Deo

Written by Pradhuman Singh

Cast Irrfan Khan (Dev Kaushal). Kirti Kulhari (Reena). Urmila Matondkar (Mili (dancer in bewafa beauty song)). Divya Dutta (Dolly Verma). Gajraj Rao (Chawla). Arunoday Singh(Ranjit Arora). Omi Vaidya (DK). Anuja Sathe (Prabha Ghatpande). Alfredo Tavares (Inspector Andrew). Neelima Azim (Dolly’s mother). Ankush Deshmukh(Office Guy). Vibha Chhibber (Blind woman). Atul Kale (BST Shankar). Mohammad Salman Khan (Salman). Abhijeet Chavan (Inspector Pramod Rawle). Pradhuman Singh(Anand Tripathi). Vikash Rajput (Vikash Rajput). Rajesh S. Khatri (Reena’s Father). Yusof Mutahar (Cameo). Anjali Ujawane (Prabha’s Mother). Tanuka Laghate (Reporter). Pravina Bhagwat Deshpande (Reena’s Mother). Manohar Teli (Prabha’s Father). Saheb Das Manik Puri (BMC Peon). Mridul Das (Mobile Store Guy). Sharad Jadhav (Constable No. 1). Monica Gupta (Maid At Dolly’s House). Priyankar Kumar (Office employee). Tanay Aul (Mall Cleaning Staff). Amit K. Sinha (Watchmen at ranjit’s bungalow). Kailash Yadav (Chanawala in Park). Monu Kumar (Mail Servant at Dolly’ House). Sandip Pandey (Guy Crying at Funeral). Raviraj Wade (Groom). Mayur Kachave (Constable No. 2). Kinjal Jain (Wife). Zaheer (Guy In Chawl). Suresh Yadav (Office Security Guard). Md. Asif Iqbal (Guy in Theatre). Shivkumar Pathak (Pandit at Funeral). Gaggan Singh(Office guy). Ruchita Wade (Bride at Marriage). Amit Kumar (Watchman At Ranjit’s Bungalow). Sanjay Kota (Auto Driver at Mall)

Languages Hindi

Producers Hanif Chunawala. Abhinay Deo. Priya Gupta. Rohit KaduDeshmukh. Hetvi Karia. Bhushan Kumar. Krishan Kumar. Akshay Powale. Apurba Sengupta. Satish Shelke

Production RDP Motion Picture. T-Series
